manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: VZAEMDEY Travel Toiletry Bag is a perfect reliable companion for travel and gym. This bag can help you organize your toiletries better. Ideal for use as a travel toiletry bag, shower bag, gym bag, swim bag, beach bag, cosmetics bag, daily necessities packaging bag, etc. This large capacity toiletry bag allows you to keep all the toiletries and cosmetics you need in different storage pockets, making your toiletries and cosmetics displayed well for easy access and saves counter space as well

High quality hardware accessories Gold nylon zipper with gold metallic nylon coil teeth. Wider size in our travel toiletry bag depth can increase the packing capacity even filled the inside of this bag with many toiletries and still zip it shut without bulky. High Performance Waterproof PU Leather The PU leather toiletry bag will carry your toiletry essentials in good organization by taking minimum space in your luggage. It's excellent quality and durable material to ensure a long lifespan. Create the Perfect Storage One main compartment with several pockets neatly organized travel-size items, such as cosmetics, lotion, shampoo, conditioner, toothbrushes and other items you need. Internal pockets made of transparent material - PVC, providing clear overview of contents.

VZAEMDEY travel toiletry bag have made heavy & inconvenient makeup organizers a story of the past! Large enough for packing and keeps good shape, buit-in hook allows hanging the toiletry kit from towel rack, coat hook or wherever is available, making your toiletries and cosmetics displayed well for easy access and saves counter space as well. It keep essentials organized neatly and safe from spilling during trips, just enjoy your romantic holidays!

reviews.reviewText: This bag is really nice and seems to be made well. The materials are thick and the zippers aren't flimsy. The inside has a lot of pockets and space for loads of large and smaller items. I can fit full size lotions, shampoos, and all of my traveling makeup in this no problem.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this bag specifically to put in my hospital bag (I’m due with my second baby in March) and I want to be more organized this time around and keep my toiletries and makeup all in one bag. For only $10 I felt like it was worth buying even if it wasn’t going to be that nice. The bag arrived today, and I was shocked when I opened it! The leather is so thick and the zipper is also very heavy duty and good quality. And it’s actually bigger than I expected! I can’t wait to use this bag, and I know it will last me a long time. Not only will it be good for my hospital stay but I could see this bag holding enough for an actual vacation as well! If you’re thinking about buying, just do it you won’t be disappointed!
